snippet: A retired married couple committed suicide Tuesday and left a note saying they were going to lose their home, helping stoke an outcry over Spain’s tough eviction laws.
lead_paragraph: A retired married couple committed suicide Tuesday and left a note saying they were going to lose their home, helping stoke an outcry over Spain’s tough eviction laws.

headline.main: Spain: Couple Commit Suicide Over Foreclosure Fear
